title: Can't see my own club as the leader
body:
I am the leader of the club "Freskeyteers" tag "Frsky" and i have not been able to see my club for some time.
and my members are saying i'm still in the club, and still the leader. What can i do to see my club again?

replies.body: Thanks for giving the name of that club! You should be able to see it now if you refresh your client.
